Making plot

penguins%>%
  ggplot(aes(x=bill_length_mm,
             y = bill_depth_mm,
             color = species)) +
  geom_point()+
  geom_smooth(method = "lm") + #add a linear regression
  labs(x = "Bill length",
       y = "Bill depth",
       color = "Species") +
  theme_grey()

penguins %>%
  group_by(species) %>%
  summarise(billmean = mean(bill_length_mm, na.rm = TRUE)) %>%
  kbl() %>%
  kable_classic() %>%
  row_spec(2, bold = T, color = "white", background = "red") %>%
  kable_styling(full_width = FALSE)
